quang-cao.html\/#Thiet_ke_website_chuyen_nghiep\" title=\"Thi\u1ebft k\u1ebf website chuy\u00ean nghi\u1ec7p\">Thi\u1ebft k\u1ebf website chuy\u00ean nghi\u1ec7p<\/a><\/li><li class='ez-toc-page-1 ez-toc-heading-level-3'><a class=\"ez-toc-link ez-toc-heading-8\" href=\"https:\/\/achaumedia.vn\/dich-vu-thiet-ke-quang-cao.html\/#Tuong_thich_voi_thiet_bi_di_dong\" title=\"T\u01b0\u01a1ng th\u00edch v\u1edbi thi\u1ebft b\u1ecb di \u0111\u1ed9ng\">T\u01b0\u01a1ng th\u00edch v\u1edbi thi\u1ebft b\u1ecb di \u0111\u1ed9ng<\/a><\/li><\/ul><\/li><\/ul><\/nav><\/div>\n\r\n<p><em>Hi\u1ec7n nay, c\u00f9ng v\u1edbi s\u1ef1 b\u00f9ng n\u1ed5 c\u1ee7a internet v\u1edbi c\u00e1c trang thi\u1ebft b\u1ecb truy c\u1eadp internet hi\u1ec7n \u0111\u1ea1i l\u00e0 nhu c\u1ea7u t\u00ecm ki\u1ebfm th\u00f4ng tin qua m\u1ea1ng c\u0169ng \u0111ang tr\u1edf th\u00e0nh th\u00f3i quen h\u00e0ng ng\u00e0y. Website l\u00e0 b\u1ed9 m\u1eb7t doanh nghi\u1ec7p c\u1ee7a b\u1ea1n tr\u00ean Internet, n\u01a1i m\u00e0 kh\u00e1ch h\u00e0ng c\u00f3 th\u1ec3 bi\u1ebft s\u1ea3n ph\u1ea9m v\u00e0 nh\u1edb \u0111\u1ebfn b\u1ea1n. V\u00ec v\u1eady m\u1ed7i m\u1ed9t doanh nghi\u1ec7p, c\u00e1 nh\u00e2n d\u00f9 l\u00e0 l\u0129nh v\u1ef1c g\u00ec n\u00ean ch\u1ecdn cho m\u00ecnh m\u1ed9t<strong> d\u1ecbch v\u1ee5 thi\u1ebft k\u1ebf qu\u1ea3ng c\u00e1o <\/strong>uy t\u00edn, ch\u1ea5t l\u01b0\u1ee3ng \u0111\u1ec3 \u0111\u1ea3m b\u1ea3o hi\u1ec7u qu\u1ea3 t\u1ed1t nh\u1ea5t.<\/em><\/p>\r\n<p><em>Nh\u1eefng g\u00ec b\u1ea1n th\u1ec3 hi\u1ec7n tr\u00ean website l\u00e0 y\u1ebfu t\u1ed1 then ch\u1ed1t \u0111\u1ec3 quy\u1ebft \u0111\u1ecbnh kh\u00e1ch h\u00e0ng c\u00f3 ch\u1ecdn b\u1ea1n hay kh\u00f4ng. M\u1ed9t\u00a0<strong>thi\u1ebft k\u1ebf website\u00a0<\/strong>\u0111\u1ed9c \u0111\u00e1o, tinh t\u1ebf s\u1ebd \u1ea3nh h\u01b0\u1edfng r\u1ea5t l\u1edbn \u0111\u1ebfn ni\u1ec1m tin v\u00e0 s\u1ef1 \u0111\u00e1nh gi\u00e1 c\u1ee7a kh\u00e1ch h\u00e0ng \u0111\u1ed1i v\u1edbi th\u01b0\u01a1ng hi\u1ec7u, s\u1ea3n ph\u1ea9m\/d\u1ecbch v\u1ee5 c\u1ee7a b\u1ea1n so v\u1edbi \u0111\u1ed1i th\u1ee7 kh\u00e1c.<\/em><\/p>\r\n<p><em>B\u1ea5t c\u1ee9 \u0111i\u1ec1u g\u00ec h\u1ecd \u0111ang ngh\u0129 t\u1edbi h\u1ecd c\u0169ng l\u00ean m\u1ea1ng t\u00ecm ki\u1ebfm \u0111i\u1ec1u n\u00e0y khi\u1ebfn c\u00e1c doanh nghi\u1ec7p kh\u00f4ng th\u1ec3 b\u1ecf qua k\u00eanh truy\u1ec1n th\u00f4ng hi\u1ec7u qu\u1ea3 ti\u1ebfp c\u1eadn ng\u01b0\u1eddi d\u00f9ng to\u00e0n c\u1ea7u qua Internet nhanh nh\u1ea5t. \u0110\u1ec3 truy\u1ec1n th\u00f4ng tr\u00ean internet c\u00f3 r\u1ea5t nhi\u1ec1u c\u00e1ch nh\u01b0ng website l\u00e0 c\u1ea7u n\u1ed1i hi\u1ec7u qu\u1ea3 v\u00e0 b\u1ec1n v\u1eefng nh\u1ea5t.<\/em><\/p>\r\n<h2><span class=\"ez-toc-section\" id=\"Van_de_ban_dang_gap_phai\"><\/span><strong>V\u1ea5n \u0111\u1ec1 b\u1ea1n \u0111ang g\u1eb7p ph\u1ea3i<\/strong><strong>?<\/strong><span class=\"ez-toc-section-end\"><\/span><\/h2>\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n<ul>\r\n<li>Website \u0111\u00e3 ho\u00e0n th\u00e0nh nh\u01b0ng l\u00e0m sao \u0111\u1ec3 \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c nhi\u1ec1u ng\u01b0\u1eddi bi\u1ebft \u0111\u1ebfn?<\/li>\r\n<li>Website c\u1ee7a b\u1ea1n \u0111\u00e3 ho\u1ea1t \u0111\u00f4ng trong th\u1eddi gian qu\u00e1 l\u00e2u nh\u01b0ng kh\u00f4ng thu h\u00fat \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c nhi\u1ec1u ng\u01b0\u1eddi truy c\u1eadp?<\/li>\r\n<li>B\u1ea1n \u0111ang c\u00f3 m\u1ed9t s\u1ea3n ph\u1ea9m m\u1edbi hay mu\u1ed1n t\u1ea1o m\u1ed9t s\u1ef1 ki\u1ec7n, ch\u01b0\u01a1ng trinh khuy\u1ebfn m\u00e3i v\u00e0 c\u1ea7n \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c nhi\u1ec1u ng\u01b0\u1eddi bi\u1ebft \u0111\u1ebfn?<\/li>\r\n<li>Vi\u1ec7c kinh doanh c\u1ee7a doanh nghi\u1ec7p b\u1ea1n ch\u01b0a hi\u1ec7u qu\u1ea3 trong m\u00f4i tr\u01b0\u1eddng intrenet?<\/li>\r\n<li>Businessmen, hand touch screen graph on a tablet<\/li>\r\n<\/ul>\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n<figure class=\"wp-block-image is-resized\"><img decoding=\"async\" class=\"wp-image-5289\" src=\"https:\/\/achaumedia.vn\/wp-content\/uploads\/2019\/10\/3666_2ca259f7cf4cbfbbca27bac259b5b1d8.jpeg\" alt=\"\" width=\"851\" srcset=\"https:\/\/achaumedia.vn\/wp-content\/uploads\/2019\/10\/3666_2ca259f7cf4cbfbbca27bac259b5b1d8.jpeg 780w, https:\/\/achaumedia.vn\/wp-content\/uploads\/2019\/10\/3666_2ca259f7cf4cbfbbca27bac259b5b1d8-300x187.jpeg 300w, https:\/\/achaumedia.vn\/wp-content\/uploads\/2019\/10\/3666_2ca259f7cf4cbfbbca27bac259b5b1d8-768x478.jpeg 768w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 780px) 100vw, 780px\" \/><\/figure>\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n<h2><span class=\"ez-toc-section\" id=\"Quy_trinh_lam_viec_cua_dich_vu_thiet_ke_quang_cao_tai_TP_HCM\"><\/span><strong>Quy tr\u00ecnh l\u00e0m vi\u1ec7c c\u1ee7a d\u1ecbch v\u1ee5 thi\u1ebft k\u1ebf qu\u1ea3ng c\u00e1o<\/strong> <strong>t\u1ea1i TP. HCM<\/strong><span class=\"ez-toc-section-end\"><\/span><\/h2>\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n<ul>\r\n<li>Ti\u1ebfp nh\u1eadn y\u00eau c\u1ea7u c\u1ee7a kh\u00e1ch h\u00e0ng.<\/li>\r\n<li>Kh\u1ea3o s\u00e1t v\u00e0 t\u00ecm hi\u1ec3u s\u1ea3n ph\u1ea9m, d\u1ecbch v\u1ee5.<\/li>\r\n<li>T\u01b0 v\u1ea5n v\u00e0 \u0111\u1ec1 xu\u1ea5t d\u1ecbch, b\u00e1o gi\u00e1 v\u1ee5 ph\u00f9 h\u1ee3p. K\u00fd h\u1ee3p \u0111\u1ed3ng h\u1ee3p t\u00e1c.<\/li>\r\n<li>Tri\u1ec3n khai d\u1ef1 \u00e1n Marketing. Nghi\u1ec7m thu v\u00e0 ho\u00e0n t\u1ea5t d\u1ef1 \u00e1n.<\/li>\r\n<\/ul>\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n<h2><span class=\"ez-toc-section\" id=\"Dich_vu_thiet_ke_to_roi\"><\/span><strong>D\u1ecbch v\u1ee5 thi\u1ebft k\u1ebf t\u1edd r\u01a1i<\/strong><span class=\"ez-toc-section-end\"><\/span><\/h2>\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n<p>D\u1ecbch v\u1ee5\u00a0<a href=\"https:\/\/achaumedia.vn\/thiet-ke-to-roi-dich-vu-thiet-ke-to-roi-gia-re-ha-noi.html\/\"><strong>thi\u1ebft k\u1ebf t\u1edd r\u01a1i, t\u1edd g\u1ea5p s\u1ea3n ph\u1ea9m<\/strong><\/a>\u00a0\u0111\u1eb9p m\u1eaft, \u1ea5n t\u01b0\u1ee3ng c\u1ee7a mang \u0111\u1ebfn cho kh\u00e1ch h\u00e0ng gi\u1ea3i ph\u00e1p ti\u1ebfp th\u1ecb s\u1ea3n ph\u1ea9m\/d\u1ecbch v\u1ee5 m\u1ed9t c\u00e1ch nhanh ch\u00f3ng, tr\u1ef1c ti\u1ebfp \u0111\u1ebfn ng\u01b0\u1eddi d\u00f9ng, kh\u00e1ch h\u00e0ng. V\u1edbi b\u1ed9 thi\u1ebft k\u1ebf t\u1edd r\u01a1i , t\u1edd g\u1ea5p qu\u1ea3ng c\u00e1o \u00fd ngh\u0129a \u0111\u1eb9p m\u1eaft th\u00ec doanh nghi\u1ec7p ho\u00e0n to\u00e0n y\u00ean t\u00e2m v\u1edbi k\u00eanh qu\u1ea3ng b\u00e1 h\u1eefu hi\u1ec7u n\u00e0y, D\u1ecbch v\u1ee5 thi\u1ebft k\u1ebf t\u1edd r\u01a1i, t\u1edd g\u1ea5p c\u1ee7a t\u1ef1 tin \u0111\u00e1p \u1ee9ng m\u1ecdi chu\u1ea9n m\u1ef1c cao nh\u1ea5t<\/p>\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n<figure class=\"wp-block-image is-resized\"><img decoding=\"async\" class=\"wp-image-5290\" src=\"https:\/\/achaumedia.vn\/wp-content\/uploads\/2019\/10\/lshriLc-1024x642.jpg\" alt=\"\" width=\"851\" srcset=\"https:\/\/achaumedia.vn\/wp-content\/uploads\/2019\/10\/lshriLc-1024x642.jpg 1024w, https:\/\/achaumedia.vn\/wp-content\/uploads\/2019\/10\/lshriLc-300x188.jpg 300w, https:\/\/achaumedia.vn\/wp-content\/uploads\/2019\/10\/lshriLc-768x481.jpg 768w, https:\/\/achaumedia.vn\/wp-content\/uploads\/2019\/10\/lshriLc.jpg 1342w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 1024px) 100vw, 1024px\" \/><\/figure>\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n<h2><span class=\"ez-toc-section\" id=\"Dich_vu_thiet_ke_logo_cong_ty\"><\/span><strong>D\u1ecbch v\u1ee5 thi\u1ebft k\u1ebf logo c\u00f4ng ty<\/strong><span class=\"ez-toc-section-end\"><\/span><\/h2>\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n<p>D\u1ecbch v\u1ee5 <a href=\"https:\/\/achaumedia.vn\/tu-van-thiet-ke-bo-nhan-dien.html\/\"><strong>thi\u1ebft k\u1ebf logo c\u00f4ng ty<\/strong><\/a><strong>\u00a0<\/strong>chuy\u00ean nghi\u1ec7p c\u1ee7a mang t\u1edbi cho doanh nghi\u1ec7p gi\u1ea3i ph\u00e1p x\u00e2y d\u1ef1ng th\u01b0\u01a1ng hi\u1ec7u chuy\u00ean nghi\u1ec7p, b\u1ec1n v\u1eefng. v\u1edbi kinh nghi\u1ec7m \u0111\u00e3 tri\u1ec3n khai tr\u00ean 8000 kh\u00e1ch h\u00e0ng v\u00e0 \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c s\u1ef1 tin t\u01b0\u1edfng c\u1ee7a tr\u00ean 5000 kh\u00e1ch h\u00e0ng, ch\u1eafc ch\u1eafn s\u1ebd \u0111em l\u1ea1i cho doanh nghi\u1ec7p nh\u1eefng m\u1eabu thi\u1ebft k\u1ebf logo c\u00f4ng ty \u0111\u1eb9p m\u1eaft, \u1ea5n t\u01b0\u1ee3ng nh\u1ea5t theo nhu c\u1ea7u c\u1ee7a doanh nghi\u1ec7p<\/p>\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n<h2><span class=\"ez-toc-section\" id=\"Dich_vu_thiet_ke_website\"><\/span><strong>D\u1ecbch v\u1ee5 thi\u1ebft k\u1ebf website<\/strong><span class=\"ez-toc-section-end\"><\/span><\/h2>\r\n<p><strong>\r\n\r\n<\/strong><\/p>\r\n<h3><span class=\"ez-toc-section\" id=\"Thiet_ke_Website\"><\/span><strong>Thi\u1ebft k\u1ebf Website<\/strong><span class=\"ez-toc-section-end\"><\/span><\/h3>\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n<p>Cung c\u1ea5p gi\u1ea3i ph\u00e1p\u00a0thi\u1ebft k\u1ebf website\u00a0theo y\u00eau c\u1ea7u,\u00a0thi\u1ebft k\u1ebf website\u00a0tr\u1ecdn g\u00f3i theo m\u1eabu gi\u00e1 r\u1ebb, nhi\u1ec1u m\u1eabu giao di\u1ec7n \u0111\u1eb9p, kh\u1ea3 n\u0103ng t\u00f9y bi\u1ebfn cao, t\u1ed1i \u01b0u h\u00f3a Onpage.<\/p>\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n<figure class=\"wp-block-image is-resized\"><img decoding=\"async\" class=\"wp-image-5291\" src=\"https:\/\/achaumedia.vn\/wp-content\/uploads\/2019\/10\/img20180904091727750-1024x603.jpg\" alt=\"\" width=\"851\" srcset=\"https:\/\/achaumedia.vn\/wp-content\/uploads\/2019\/10\/img20180904091727750.jpg 1024w, https:\/\/achaumedia.vn\/wp-content\/uploads\/2019\/10\/img20180904091727750-300x177.jpg 300w, https:\/\/achaumedia.vn\/wp-content\/uploads\/2019\/10\/img20180904091727750-768x452.jpg 768w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 1024px) 100vw, 1024px\" \/><\/figure>\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n<h3><span class=\"ez-toc-section\" id=\"Thiet_ke_website_chuyen_nghiep\"><\/span><strong>Thi\u1ebft k\u1ebf website chuy\u00ean nghi\u1ec7p<\/strong><span class=\"ez-toc-section-end\"><\/span><\/h3>\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n<p>\u0110\u1ed9i ng\u0169 thi\u1ebft k\u1ebf gi\u00e0u kinh nghi\u1ec7m, mang \u0111\u1ebfn b\u1ea3n thi\u1ebft k\u1ebf giao di\u1ec7n web chuy\u00ean nghi\u1ec7p, s\u00e1ng t\u1ea1o, v\u1edbi thi\u1ebft k\u1ebf ph\u1eb3ng theo phong c\u00e1ch m\u1edbi. <a href=\"https:\/\/achaumedia.vn\/dich-vu-thiet-ke-website.html\/\">D\u1ecbch v\u1ee5 thi\u1ebft k\u1ebf website<\/a> c\u1ee7a \u00c1 Ch\u00e2u Media s\u1ebd gi\u00fap website c\u1ee7a b\u1ea1n t\u1ea1o ra nh\u1eefng tr\u1ea3i nghi\u1ec7m v\u00e0 t\u01b0\u01a1ng t\u00e1c t\u1ed1t v\u1edbi kh\u00e1ch h\u00e0ng.<\/p>\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n<h3><span class=\"ez-toc-section\" id=\"Tuong_thich_voi_thiet_bi_di_dong\"><\/span><strong>T\u01b0\u01a1ng th\u00edch v\u1edbi thi\u1ebft b\u1ecb di \u0111\u1ed9ng<\/strong><span class=\"ez-toc-section-end\"><\/span><\/h3>\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n<p>C\u00f4ng ngh\u1ec7 thi\u1ebft k\u1ebf web responsive s\u1ebd gi\u00fap giao di\u1ec7n web ch\u1ea1y tr\u00ean m\u1ecdi thi\u1ebft b\u1ecb di \u0111\u1ed9ng. Mobile Friendly website xu h\u01b0\u1edbng ph\u00e1t tri\u1ec3n web tr\u00ean to\u00e0n th\u1ebf gi\u1edbi, \u0111\u00e2y l\u00e0 ti\u00eau ch\u00ed \u0111\u00e1nh gi\u00e1 c\u1ee7a Google gi\u00fap website c\u1ea3i thi\u1ec7n t\u1ed1t h\u01a1n tr\u00ean Google rank.<\/p>\r\n","protected":false},"excerpt":{"rendered":"<p>Hi\u1ec7n nay, c\u00f9ng v\u1edbi s\u1ef1 b\u00f9ng n\u1ed5 c\u1ee7a internet v\u1edbi c\u00e1c trang thi\u1ebft b\u1ecb truy c\u1eadp internet hi\u1ec7n \u0111\u1ea1i l\u00e0 nhu c\u1ea7u t\u00ecm ki\u1ebfm th\u00f4ng tin qua m\u1ea1ng c\u0169ng \u0111ang tr\u1edf th\u00e0nh th\u00f3i quen h\u00e0ng ng\u00e0y. Website l\u00e0 b\u1ed9 m\u1eb7t doanh nghi\u1ec7p c\u1ee7a b\u1ea1n tr\u00ean Internet, n\u01a1i m\u00e0 kh\u00e1ch h\u00e0ng c\u00f3 th\u1ec3 bi\u1ebft s\u1ea3n ph\u1ea9m&#8230;<\/p>\n","protected":false},"author":1,"featured_media":5291,"comment_status":"open","ping_status":"open","sticky":false,"template":"","format":"standard","meta":[],"categories":[73,77],"tags":[338,379,105,114],"yoast_head":"<!-- This site is optimized with the Yoast SEO Premium plugin v18.7 (Yoast SEO v19.9) - https:\/\/yoast.com\/wordpress\/plugins\/seo\/ -->\n<title>D\u1ecbch V\u1ee5 Thi\u1ebft K\u1ebf Qu\u1ea3ng C\u00e1o Online t\u1ea1i TP.HCM - \u00c1 Ch\u00e2u Multimedia<\/title>\n<meta name=\"description\" content=\"D\u1ecbch v\u1ee5 thi\u1ebft k\u1ebf qu\u1ea3ng c\u00e1o quan trong nh\u01b0 th\u1ebf n\u00e0o \